Articles.Content: 1016:
1017: Sun got stuck in the mud.
1018: Suddenly, homestucks.
1019: This is the bathroom floor. You work here.

1020: You see Thranduil jousting with Harry Potter's dad.

(Get it?)
1021: You see agents of the Protectors of the Plot continuum charging downwards to floor 1020 to stop the slash fiction.
1022: This is the room filled with 350,000,000 potatoes. Move along...
1023: Your getting so high up the first few floors start to unload.
1024: you see Kaname and Prof. endwalker getting shot at by a firing squad for necroing this thread
1025: this floor is in the shape of a tesseract, it's quite mind bending.
1026: The docking bay for the NX-01 enterprise, the Enterprise is missing, however, and there's a big hole in the roof, which means someone has lodged it in floor 1028

1027: You suddenly find yourself in black and white, and you hear an eerily familiar tune......

That's it! You snap your fingers as you remember. That tune is The Twilight Zone....
1028: the USS enterprise from 1026 is being used as a protest hub, alongside the IXS enterprise, which docks here. the protest is about the locking of Kerbal history
1029: You see a few sleepless teenagers playing Beta than Ever instead of doing homework.
1030: This room is filled with toy models of the warpship Phoenix, all piled up in the center, there is a big hole on the ceiling and light is leaking through.
1031: This is where we keep the wormhole between Earth and Kerbin. Oh yeah, watch out for the Kosmos satellite!
1032: It's a museum of warp technology, The models are form the Phoenix all the way to the Enterprise J, beside the Phoenix is the IXS enterprise, and beside that is the XCV-330.
1033: A group is playing DMP KSP and having a war, also with huge battlestations (as in computers with flight monitors and controls and such.).
1034: Look out a window, and see... Wait... OHKRAKEN THATS JEB FLYING TOWARDS US IN A JET RUUUUUUUUUUUNNNNNN
1035: Nothing is here except complete blackness. I think the Kraken has struck here!
1036: More models of the Phoenix reside here. Lots more.
1037: jebs nukes
1038: Better get those hazmat suits out, because this room is filled with RADIATION!!!
1039: Danny tells you the exit is on floor 100000000. he teleports you up there for half a second to be sure
1040: Male underwear, household appliances, bathrooms.
